023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-beta-dates-and-codes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-beta-dates-and-codes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-beta-dates-and-codes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-beta-dates-and-codes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507824" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视暴雪。</figcaption></figure><p>竞争与市场管理局一直是微软努力中最难说服的参与者之一。</p><p>今年 2 月，它要求<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-told-to-remove-call-of-duty-from-activision-acquisition-by-uk-regulators-3394664">动视公司剥离<em>《使命召唤》</em>以使收购获得批准</a>，但当微软表示该系列仍将在多个平台上停留十年时，它改变了立场。</p><p>然后，在四月份，监管机构驳回了此次收购，并指出微软目前在云游戏领域的实力只有动视暴雪纳入其投资组合才能增强。</p><p>它还阻止了微软在未经竞争和市场管理局提前批准的情况下试图收购动视暴雪。 </p><figure id="attachment_3493376" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3493376" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3493376" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/google-is-disrupting-the-games-industry-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3493376" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox 控制器 图片来源：Lang 5，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>然而， <a href="htt